01:16:33,833 --> 01:16:34,875
Kaneda!

1021
01:16:51,291 --> 01:16:53,875
Kay! What's wrong?

1022
01:16:58,125 --> 01:17:01,250
That night. You were there.

1023
01:17:04,916 --> 01:17:06,041
Wait.

1024
01:17:12,291 --> 01:17:13,416
Kay!

1025
01:17:17,416 --> 01:17:18,875
Th-They're gone.

1026
01:17:20,625 --> 01:17:23,541
You're the one, right? You
changed my friend, didn't you?

1027
01:17:23,625 --> 01:17:26,958
The thing about Akira's power
is it exists within everyone

1028
01:17:27,041 --> 01:17:28,458
from the start.

1029
01:17:28,541 --> 01:17:30,833
Hey, who is that? Huh?

1030
01:17:30,916 --> 01:17:33,958
But, when that power
is awakened inside,

1031
01:17:34,041 --> 01:17:37,708
it is important to wisely
choose how to use it.

1032
01:17:37,791 --> 01:17:40,208
When the time comes,
you might not know it

1033
01:17:40,291 --> 01:17:43,458
