1034
01:17:43,541 --> 01:17:46,291
Your friend has
already made his choice.

1035
01:17:47,875 --> 01:17:51,708
Tetsuo is our newest companion.
He's our friend, also.

1036
01:17:53,500 --> 01:17:55,250
His actions are out of control,

1037
