1120
01:25:50,083 --> 01:25:52,625
His present position is-- Ha-- 

1121
01:25:52,708 --> 01:25:57,583
coordinates 99871 by 4332.

1122
01:25:57,666 --> 01:25:59,125
That's about
two kilometers south of

1123
01:25:59,208 --> 01:26:01,541
