1134
01:27:41,708 --> 01:27:42,625
Huh?

1135
01:27:47,458 --> 01:27:50,291
You were the girl
that was with Kaneda.

1136
01:27:50,375 --> 01:27:55,125
You shouldn't use your power in
this way for it is not correct.

1137
01:27:55,208 --> 01:27:56,500
What's that?

1138
01:27:56,583 --> 01:27:59,083
Because in the end you won't
be able to control it

1139
01:27:59,166 --> 01:28:01,000
and it will control you.

1140
