It's the kids talking.
You're those brats, right?

1141
01:28:22,500 --> 01:28:24,375
Nice one.

1142
01:28:56,541 --> 01:28:59,958
Wait, Colonel.
It's not safe here.

1143
01:29:41,000 --> 01:29:43,708
Alright now, next move.

1144
01:31:10,416 --> 01:31:12,250
Open now!

1145
01:31:22,708 --> 01:31:25,000
What the hell is this?

1146
01:31:25,083 --> 01:31:27,583
That is Akira
before you, Tetsuo.

1147
01:31:27,666 --> 01:31:30,958
That's the Akira you wanted
to meet. There is your messiah.

1148
01:31:31,041 --> 01:31:33,833
The chosen one that
you've been looking for.

1149
01:31:33,916 --> 01:31:36,416
Not long after
his transcendental awakening,

1150
01:31:36,500 --> 01:31:38,083
his organs and tissues
were subjected

1151
