to ever test known
to modern science.

1152
01:31:40,000 --> 01:31:43,916
He's dead. That's it.
What you see now lying there

1153
01:31:44,000 --> 01:31:45,708
is all that's left of him.

1154
01:31:54,708 --> 01:31:56,666
And all of the
scientists back then

