and test samples
to future generations

1158
01:32:03,375 --> 01:32:06,375
by preserving them in frozen
capsules and locking them away.

1159
01:32:08,875 --> 01:32:10,791
SOL. We will use SOL.

1160
01:32:13,583 --> 01:32:16,583
Akira has been dead all this
time and now you know the truth.

1161
01:32:16,666 --> 01:32:19,666
Well, are you
satisfied now, Tetsuo?

1162
01:32:24,583 --> 01:32:27,041
Now, will you return with us?

1163
01:32:27,125 --> 01:32:29,208
Like hell!

1164
01:32:29,291 --> 01:32:32,166
Contact the Central Defense
Center, and tell them

1165
01:32:32,250 --> 01:32:34,291
to patch us through into
SOL's major control curcuits,

1166
01:32:34,375 --> 01:32:34,958
right away!

1167
01:32:35,041 --> 01:32:35,791
Yes, sir.

1168
01:32:47,750 --> 01:32:49,333
Asshole! Watch it.

1169
01:32:53,125 --> 01:32:54,250
Hey, watch it jerk.

1170
01:32:54,333 --> 01:32:58,291
Dammit, move!
Get out of the way. Move it.

1171
01:33:14,833 --> 01:33:17,541
