1185
01:34:24,333 --> 01:34:25,750
Tetsuo!

1186
01:34:49,583 --> 01:34:51,250
Son of a bitch.

1187
01:35:04,541 --> 01:35:05,625
Kay!

1188
01:35:07,541 --> 01:35:08,625
Aww dammit.

1189
01:35:12,625 --> 01:35:14,583
Let's do it.

1190
01:35:25,791 --> 01:35:27,375
Haha, gotcha!

1191
01:35:28,583 --> 01:35:29,458
What?

1192
01:35:29,541 --> 01:35:30,958
Huh?

1193
01:35:34,291 --> 01:35:36,125
The damn battery's dead.

1194
01:35:36,208 --> 01:35:38,000
What's the matter now Kaneda?

1195
01:35:38,083 --> 01:35:44,166
Ah dammit! It aint fair, Tetsuo.
Fight with your bare hands.

1196
01:35:46,916 --> 01:35:48,333
Oh, this is funny.

1197
01:35:50,291 --> 01:35:53,375
Feeling frustrated, Kaneda?
Now do you understand

1198
01:35:53,458 --> 01:35:56,208
