1214
01:38:22,458 --> 01:38:23,916
Kaneda!

1215
01:38:24,000 --> 01:38:27,166
Wha? Kai! Kay!

1216
01:38:27,250 --> 01:38:27,833
Kaneda!

1217
01:38:27,916 --> 01:38:28,708
Kaneda hurry!

1218
01:38:28,791 --> 01:38:30,333
Get on! Get on!

1219
01:38:30,416 --> 01:38:31,541
