When Tetsuo's power
reaches it's peak?

1224
01:39:37,000 --> 01:39:38,833
Is that what you're thinking?

1225
01:39:38,916 --> 01:39:43,916
That's when we do it,
but will it really work?

1226
01:39:44,000 --> 01:39:46,708
We know the future
doesn't necessarily

1227
01:39:46,791 --> 01:39:49,041
proceed along a single course.

1228
01:39:49,125 --> 01:39:51,250
There ought to be
a future we can choose.

1229
01:39:51,333 --> 01:39:53,166
It's up to us to find it.

1230
01:40:02,875 --> 01:40:04,541
What's Tetsuo's status, Doctor?

1231
01:40:04,625 --> 01:40:08,333
Ah, Colonel. We set up
a camera in the stadium

1232
01:40:08,416 --> 01:40:09,916
if you want to check.

