1234
01:40:13,208 --> 01:40:16,666
Colonel, you must take a look
at this data. It's phenomenal!

1235
01:40:16,750 --> 01:40:19,333
We're still analyzing the energy
given off by the subject

1236
01:40:19,416 --> 01:40:21,291
but it's just magnificent!

1237
01:40:21,375 --> 01:40:24,750
Oh yes, wonderful.
Of course, this is clearly

1238
01:40:24,833 --> 01:40:26,208
a proton collapse.

1239
01:40:26,291 --> 01:40:28,416
We're also detecting a fair
number of what we believe

1240
01:40:28,500 --> 01:40:30,750
to be unknown
particles to science.

1241
01:40:30,833 --> 01:40:32,208
If we could put this into

1242
01:40:32,291 --> 01:40:35,375
a theoretical framework then
physics, quantum physics,

1243
01:40:35,458 --> 01:40:38,875
humanity itself could know
the fundamental truths--

