1246
01:40:51,916 --> 01:40:54,708
What tha? The pattern!

1247
01:40:57,708 --> 01:40:59,958
You bastard,
what did I tell you?

1248
01:41:00,041 --> 01:41:02,833
But Colonel,
I couldn't throw away such

1249
01:41:02,916 --> 01:41:05,500
a magnificent subject--

1250
01:41:05,583 --> 01:41:06,833
Shut up!

1251
01:41:29,500 --> 01:41:32,375
