01:41:44,541 --> 01:41:45,708
Yeah, you did.

1258
01:41:45,791 --> 01:41:47,250
Uh, by the way your bike's
still on fire.

1259
01:41:47,333 --> 01:41:49,708
Huh? Oh! Oh man.

1260
01:42:29,375 --> 01:42:31,083
Tetsuo?

1261
01:42:42,708 --> 01:42:46,916
Tetsuo, why is everyone calling
you Akira? What does it mean?

