He never existed.

1263
01:42:51,541 --> 01:42:53,833
It doesn't matter who he is,
they don't care

1264
01:42:56,375 --> 01:42:59,125
just so long as
he destroys things.

1265
01:42:59,208 --> 01:43:01,791
What's that? Your arm!
Look at it!

1266
01:43:01,875 --> 01:43:05,833
Well, it doesn't look like much
