01:43:13,291 --> 01:43:15,166
It's nothing!

1269
01:43:15,250 --> 01:43:16,125
Tetsuo, I just--

1270
01:43:16,208 --> 01:43:18,458
Shut up! Just go away!

1271
01:43:25,458 --> 01:43:26,625
Medicine.

1272
01:43:27,708 --> 01:43:31,208
What's wrong, Tetsuo?
Are you in pain?

1273
01:43:31,291 --> 01:43:34,916
Go back to the lab
and get that medicine.

1274
01:43:35,000 --> 01:43:36,916
Doctor, did you hear that?

1275
01:43:37,000 --> 01:43:38,333
I did, Colonel.

1276
01:43:38,416 --> 01:43:40,083
Well, any signs of it?

1277
01:43:41,083 --> 01:43:43,958
Well I can't be entirely certain
here, but it seems that

1278
01:43:44,041 --> 01:43:46,083
the power which had been
held back by the drugs

1279
01:43:46,166 --> 01:43:47,375
is breaking free.

1280
01:43:47,458 --> 01:43:49,125
He may not be able
to control the power

1281
01:43:49,208 --> 01:43:51,000
that has awakened so suddenly.

1282
01:43:51,083 --> 01:43:53,500
He's in an extremely
critical condition.

1283
01:43:54,833 --> 01:43:57,625
Come back to the lab
and receive proper treatment.

1284
01:43:57,708 --> 01:43:59,041
If you don't you may die.

1285
01:44:02,333 --> 01:44:04,041
You want me to enroll
in your kindergarten

1286
01:44:04,125 --> 01:44:06,000
and live happily
ever after, huh?

1287
01:44:06,083 --> 01:44:07,916
Be quiet and do
what you're told?

1288
01:44:08,000 --> 01:44:10,083
Take your medicine every day
and end up all shriveled

1289
01:44:10,166 --> 01:44:11,625
like those kids?

1290
01:44:16,916 --> 01:44:20,083
Kaori. Kaori!

1291
01:44:22,041 --> 01:44:25,000
Medicine, please.

1292
01:44:25,083 --> 01:44:26,666
N-No.

1293
01:44:26,750 --> 01:44:28,375
Stop Tetsuo!

1294
01:44:29,791 --> 01:44:30,958
Tetsuo!

1295
01:44:33,333 --> 01:44:34,500
Tets--

1296
01:45:06,166 --> 01:45:07,375
Kaneda!

1297
01:45:54,541 --> 01:45:57,333
Son of a-- Huh?

1298
01:46:00,083 --> 01:46:02,333
What are you three doing here?

1299
01:46:08,458 --> 01:46:10,291
You didn't learn
your lesson, huh?

1300
01:46:12,583 --> 01:46:14,041
Heads up, Tetsuo!

1301
01:46:28,583 --> 01:46:30,000
Takashi!

1302
01:46:32,500 --> 01:46:33,958
Akira's here.

1303
01:46:47,250 --> 01:46:51,458
Help! Kaneda, help please!

1304
01:47:01,000 --> 01:47:03,625
Kaori.

1305
01:47:05,750 --> 01:47:09,083
Please. Help me.

1306
01:47:12,750 --> 01:47:14,250
Help me!

1307
01:47:22,166 --> 01:47:23,708
Let her go!

1308
01:47:41,125 --> 01:47:44,833
Kaori. Kaori. Kaori!

1309
01:47:44,916 --> 01:47:47,541
Tetsuo! Are you there?

1310
01:47:47,625 --> 01:47:50,750
Kaori. Kaori's gonna die!

1311
01:47:50,833 --> 01:47:53,541
What? What did you say?

1312
01:47:53,625 --> 01:47:57,166
My body's not doing
what I tell it to.

1313
01:47:57,250 --> 01:47:59,291
My power's acting on it's own.

1314
01:47:59,375 --> 01:48:01,041
Kaori! Ah!

1315
01:48:02,291 --> 01:48:06,125
Kaori's dying. Kaneda. Help me.

1316
01:48:06,208 --> 01:48:10,208
Stop this, Tetsuo! Stop it now!

1317
01:48:10,291 --> 01:48:15,833
Kaori's pain...
is coming into me. Ahh!

1318
01:48:15,916 --> 01:48:18,375
Tetsuo!

1319
01:48:18,458 --> 01:48:22,125
Kaneda! Run away!

1320
01:48:35,875 --> 01:48:38,250
Tetsuo!

1321
01:48:49,125 --> 01:48:52,958
Kiyoko, Takashi, Masaru!
Hurry, get away from here!

1322
01:48:57,208 --> 01:48:58,333
Come on.

1323
01:49:04,541 --> 01:49:07,750
I can't believe it.
It's as if--

1324
01:49:20,458 --> 01:49:23,166
Kiyoko! Taka--

1325
01:49:57,625 --> 01:50:01,583
Hi. Akira.

1326
01:50:10,083 --> 01:50:12,291
Oh no. That's the--

1327
01:50:13,291 --> 01:50:15,041
But that's impossible!

1328
01:50:25,208 --> 01:50:26,833
W-Where am I?

1329
01:50:27,833 --> 01:50:31,750
Hurry. Get into the tunnel.
You'll be safe in there.

1330
01:50:31,833 --> 01:50:34,000
Kiyoko. Where are you?

1331
01:50:48,291 --> 01:50:50,000
Tetsuo!

1332
01:50:50,083 --> 01:50:52,625
Kaneda!

1333
01:50:52,708 --> 01:50:54,291
Hang on!

1334
01:50:56,208 --> 01:50:57,791
Hurry, you gotta
get out of here.

1335
01:50:57,875 --> 01:50:59,541
Go away.

1336
01:50:59,625 --> 01:51:00,541
Tetsuo!

1337
01:51:00,625 --> 01:51:02,416
Don't go near it!

1338
01:51:08,708 --> 01:51:11,208
No don't! Wait, Takashi!

1339
01:51:11,291 --> 01:51:14,916
If you went in now you'd
be trapped along with him.

1340
01:51:15,000 --> 01:51:19,083
But he-- none of this
is his fault at all.

1341
01:51:26,166 --> 01:51:27,166
Takashi!

1342
01:51:27,250 --> 01:51:28,833
Takashi!

1343
01:51:35,166 --> 01:51:39,625
If we went in there
we wouldn't be strong enough

1344
01:51:39,708 --> 01:51:41,458
to come back out again.

1345
01:51:42,541 --> 01:51:46,625
But if the three of us tried,
maybe we could save that boy.

1346
01:51:46,708 --> 01:51:50,166
You're right. Us three together.

1347
01:51:59,291 --> 01:52:03,083
Look at that. We should get out
of here now. H-Hey!

1348
01:52:04,541 --> 01:52:06,250
Kaneda's in there.

1349
01:52:39,166 --> 01:52:42,375
You see that? You're not revving
your engine enough already.

1350
01:52:42,458 --> 01:52:47,250
When you go into a corner,
lean in suicidally. Watch.

1351
01:52:47,333 --> 01:52:48,666
What the hell do you call that?

1352
01:52:48,750 --> 01:52:51,000
Cornering, man.

1353
01:52:51,083 --> 01:52:52,583
You got it, Tetsuo?

1354
01:52:59,708 --> 01:53:01,750
Hey look,
they brought another kid.

1355
01:53:01,833 --> 01:53:03,500
Is he a transfer student?

1356
01:53:03,583 --> 01:53:04,958
His mom and dad left him.

1357
01:53:05,041 --> 01:53:07,041
You can see it in his face.

1358
01:53:10,083 --> 01:53:13,458
Are these-- Are these all of
your dreams and memories,

1359
01:53:13,541 --> 01:53:15,166
Tetsuo?

1360
01:53:16,208 --> 01:53:17,875
W-Wait!

1361
01:54:35,166 --> 01:54:37,958
Is this Akira?

1362
01:54:38,041 --> 01:54:41,291
Yes. We called him here
to the three of us.

1363
01:54:41,375 --> 01:54:43,875
He's going to
take Tetsuo with him.

1364
01:54:43,958 --> 01:54:47,083
Take him where? Where?

1365
01:54:47,166 --> 01:54:51,208
It's too much for Tetsuo.
And for the three of us also.

1366
01:54:51,291 --> 01:54:53,000
And Akira, too.

1367
01:54:53,083 --> 01:54:56,791
It's way too big for us
as we are now.

1368
01:54:56,875 --> 01:55:00,625
But someday we ought
to be able to--

1369
01:55:00,708 --> 01:55:04,166
because it has already begun.

1370
01:55:04,250 --> 01:55:06,625
Your friend, she's--

1371
01:55:06,708 --> 01:55:12,458
My friend. Kay. It's Kay
you're talking about.

1372
01:55:37,875 --> 01:55:39,666
Tetsuo.

1373
01:55:44,125 --> 01:55:45,750
This is yours, right?

1374
01:55:51,916 --> 01:55:54,791
They're always like that
with the new kids.

1375
01:55:54,875 --> 01:55:57,041
Hey, you came today, right?

1376
01:55:57,125 --> 01:56:01,166
They beat me up too. But the
truth is, those guys are wimps.

1377
01:56:01,250 --> 01:56:07,291
My name is...
Tetsuo. Tetsuo Shima.

1378
01:56:07,375 --> 01:56:12,291
The truth is, I just got here
myself. My name is--

1379
01:56:12,375 --> 01:56:17,958
Kaneda. Kaneda. Kaneda!

1380
01:56:18,041 --> 01:56:19,333
Kay.

1381
01:56:45,791 --> 01:56:49,416
What in the world is
happening? What's this?

1382
01:56:51,541 --> 01:56:56,208
This is-- If this is correct,
it's showing that this

1383
01:56:56,291 --> 01:56:58,708
is the birth of the universe!

1384
01:57:04,458 --> 01:57:07,125
Kay!

1385
01:57:13,208 --> 01:57:19,583
What's going on here? Ahh!
Disappearing. It's disappearing!

1386
01:58:30,416 --> 01:58:32,750
Kaneda can you hear me?

1387
01:58:56,000 --> 01:58:58,166
Tetsuo.

1388
01:59:00,500 --> 01:59:02,333
Kaneda, what is--?

1389
01:59:03,500 --> 01:59:04,750
Thank you.

1390
01:59:04,833 --> 01:59:06,083
Huh?

1391
01:59:06,166 --> 01:59:09,625
You called me, didn't you?
And I heard you.

1392
01:59:16,500 --> 01:59:19,375
Kaneda. Oh my.

1393
01:59:19,458 --> 01:59:21,000
Where's Tetsuo?

1394
01:59:22,125 --> 01:59:28,166
He just left. Those kids
did too. Akira also.

1395
01:59:28,250 --> 01:59:30,583
Kaneda, back then--
Did you just--?

1396
01:59:30,666 --> 01:59:38,916
Kaneda! You're alive!
I thought you were in there.

1397
01:59:39,000 --> 01:59:41,333
I thought you were
in there for sure.

1398
01:59:44,625 --> 01:59:49,125
Tetsuo! What happened to
Tetsuo? Is he-- dead?

1399
01:59:49,208 --> 01:59:52,458
I'm not sure. S-Something--

1400
02:00:18,458 --> 02:00:22,291
But someday
we ought to be able to--

1401
02:00:22,375 --> 02:00:25,625
because it has already begun.

1402
02:00:43,458 --> 02:00:46,875
I am. Tetsuo.

